*spice-0.7.2 (05 Feb 2011)

  05 Feb 2011; Tiziano Müller <dev-zero@gentoo.org> +spice-0.7.2.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  05 Jan 2011; Tiziano Müller <dev-zero@gentoo.org> spice-0.7.1.ebuild,
